Hey, that's really neat.

01:34.177 --> 01:36.137
Thanks. It's the

01:34.177 --> 01:36.137
USS  Constitution.

01:36.179 --> 01:38.057
In 1803, it sailed all the...

01:38.097 --> 01:39.516
Typhoon!

01:39.558 --> 01:40.976
I can't believe you did that!

