01:59.912 --> 02:00.955
What is?

02:00.996 --> 02:02.414
I wished as hard as I could

02:02.456 --> 02:05.166
and Reese completely

02:02.456 --> 02:05.166
disappeared.

02:05.208 --> 02:06.460
Yeah, yeah, very funny.

02:06.501 --> 02:09.170
Huh. The smell is gone, too.

02:09.212 --> 02:11.548
I wonder if it works

02:09.212 --> 02:11.548
on other things.

02:11.590 --> 02:14.927
Nah. If this were gone,

02:11.590 --> 02:14.927
I'd miss it.

02:22.935 --> 02:24.227
(screams)

02:24.269 --> 02:26.229
You have your father's breasts.

02:26.271 --> 02:27.481
For God's sake,

02:26.271 --> 02:27.481
Mother,

02:27.522 --> 02:29.608
