02:31.860 --> 02:33.194
I'm sorry.

02:33.236 --> 02:35.447
You scared the living

02:33.236 --> 02:35.447
daylights out of me.

02:35.489 --> 02:36.573
I have news.

02:36.615 --> 02:38.075
Look, if Susan kicked you out,

02:38.117 --> 02:39.576
it doesn't mean

02:38.117 --> 02:39.576
you can stay here,

02:39.618 --> 02:41.036
because we just don't have

02:39.618 --> 02:41.036
the room.

02:41.078 --> 02:42.370
Not with the new baby and all.

02:42.412 --> 02:44.456
Oh, yes, another precious baby.

02:44.498 --> 02:47.084
You wouldn't want

02:44.498 --> 02:47.084
