02:47.126 --> 02:49.878
I'm not moving in.

02:47.126 --> 02:49.878
I'm getting married.

02:49.920 --> 02:51.713
What?!

02:51.755 --> 02:54.008
His name is Mr. Li.

02:54.049 --> 02:56.217
I met him on my Alaska cruise.

02:56.259 --> 02:57.302
We're getting married tomorrow.

02:59.096 --> 03:00.806
You're getting married

02:59.096 --> 03:00.806
tomorrow?!

03:00.848 --> 03:02.683
At my age, if he has his teeth

03:02.724 --> 03:04.518
and is good in bed, why wait?

03:04.559 --> 03:05.226
(groans)

03:05.268 --> 03:06.812
Oh, I forgot.

03:06.854 --> 03:08.730
This one doesn't

03:06.854 --> 03:08.730
