03:08.772 --> 03:10.649
Grandma, I'm not gay.

03:10.691 --> 03:12.609
That's right.

03:10.691 --> 03:12.609
I'm just a liar.

03:12.651 --> 03:15.529
You'll be giving the rehearsal

03:12.651 --> 03:15.529
dinner here tonight.

03:15.570 --> 03:17.531
Tonight? Is Susan coming?

03:17.572 --> 03:21.076
No. Maybe next time

03:17.572 --> 03:21.076
your sister will think twice

03:21.118 --> 03:23.162
before she yells the answer

03:21.118 --> 03:23.162
to  Wheel of Fortune.

03:23.202 --> 03:24.245
Give someone else a chance.

03:24.287 --> 03:25.413
Wedding's at

03:24.287 --> 03:25.413
