03:26.707 --> 03:28.249
to Hong Kong.

03:28.291 --> 03:30.251
You're going to Hong Kong?

03:30.293 --> 03:32.253
Yes. He has a house

03:30.293 --> 03:32.253
there. That's where

03:30.293 --> 03:32.253
we're going to live.

03:32.295 --> 03:33.547
You're moving to China?

03:33.588 --> 03:35.174
I know.

03:35.215 --> 03:37.509
Chickens in the streets,

03:35.215 --> 03:37.509
children in the sweatshops,

03:37.551 --> 03:39.178
everyone smokes.

03:39.219 --> 03:40.888
It's a dream come true.

03:40.929 --> 03:43.182
It's just so sudden.

03:43.223 --> 03:45.266
I understand

03:43.223 --> 03:45.266
it is hard for you.

03:45.308 --> 03:48.311
I know how much

03:45.308 --> 03:48.311
you loved your father.

03:48.353 --> 03:51.314
Yes, that's probably it.

03:53.316 --> 03:55.276
Can you believe this?

03:55.318 --> 03:56.904
She'll be almost exactly

03:56.945 --> 03:58.572
on the other side

03:56.945 --> 03:58.572
of the Earth.

03:58.613 --> 04:00.115
We'll be separated from her

04:00.157 --> 04:02.283
by the entire molten core

04:00.157 --> 04:02.283
of a planet.

04:02.325 --> 04:04.703
It's like Christmas!

04:06.705 --> 04:10.291
Francis, I've done something

04:06.705 --> 04:10.291
