04:10.333 --> 04:13.128
I hired an acting group

04:13.170 --> 04:17.007
to stage a murder-

04:13.170 --> 04:17.007
mystery weekend.

04:17.049 --> 04:18.341
Oh, dear God.

04:18.383 --> 04:21.136
The best part is, the

04:18.383 --> 04:21.136
actors will be checking in

04:21.178 --> 04:22.512
as regular guests.

04:22.554 --> 04:24.765
They could be

04:22.554 --> 04:24.765
among us right now

04:24.806 --> 04:26.558
and we would never know it.

04:26.600 --> 04:27.893
(man clears throat)

04:27.935 --> 04:29.477
