04:47.370 --> 04:48.705
Oh, great.

04:48.747 --> 04:50.040
HAL:

04:48.747 --> 04:50.040
Honey, don't worry.

04:50.082 --> 04:51.625
Everything's going

04:50.082 --> 04:51.625
to be fine.

04:51.666 --> 04:54.169
Just relax and let's

04:51.666 --> 04:54.169
have a nice dinner.

04:54.753 --> 04:56.546
Ida's quite a catch!

04:57.380 --> 04:59.216
Hi, I'm Lois.

04:57.380 --> 04:59.216
This is Hal.

04:59.258 --> 05:00.425
Welcome to our home.

05:00.467 --> 05:02.343
MR. LI:

05:00.467 --> 05:02.343
Hello. Nice to meet you both.

05:02.385 --> 05:03.344
Get your coat?

05:03.386 --> 05:04.387
Stay away from me.

05:04.429 --> 05:05.931
Ooh. Strong and independent.

05:05.973 --> 05:08.016
Yet not so independent

05:05.973 --> 05:08.016
that she won't be

05:08.058 --> 05:09.810
a fully participating partner

05:08.058 --> 05:09.810
in your marriage.

05:09.851 --> 05:11.979
Shut up. You're blithering

05:09.851 --> 05:11.979
