05:12.020 --> 05:14.273
And delightfully honest.

05:14.314 --> 05:18.026
How can you be so callous,

05:14.314 --> 05:18.026
Cedric?!

05:19.278 --> 05:20.737
CEDRIC: I told you

05:19.278 --> 05:20.737
