An old English hunting lodge

05:30.413 --> 05:36.419
can be a  very  dangerous place.

05:36.461 --> 05:38.546
Please, can't you get these

05:36.461 --> 05:38.546
morons out of here?

05:38.588 --> 05:40.590
I know.

05:38.588 --> 05:40.590
I'm very sorry.

05:40.632 --> 05:41.633
Just... try to ignore them.

