That's it.

06:00.902 --> 06:02.403
We're checking out.

06:02.445 --> 06:03.404
No!

06:03.446 --> 06:05.406
Please, wait.

06:05.448 --> 06:07.909
Otto, you have

06:05.448 --> 06:07.909
to stop this.

06:07.951 --> 06:09.870
It's ruining

06:07.951 --> 06:09.870
everyone's time.

06:09.911 --> 06:11.872
Francis, try to be

06:09.911 --> 06:11.872
more understanding.

06:11.913 --> 06:13.832
They may be

06:11.913 --> 06:13.832
a little under-rehearsed,

06:13.874 --> 06:15.458
but they're working

06:13.874 --> 06:15.458
with us.

06:15.500 --> 06:18.419
They were completely open

06:15.500 --> 06:18.419
to cutting the musical numbers.

06:18.461 --> 06:20.421
Our guests are

06:18.461 --> 06:20.421
leaving in droves.

06:20.463 --> 06:22.632
We lost 12 in

06:20.463 --> 06:22.632
the last hour alone.

06:24.467 --> 06:27.012
I am not a big game hunter,

06:27.054 --> 06:31.390
I am actually

06:27.054 --> 06:31.390
a police inspector.

06:32.100 --> 06:35.436
Specialty... murder.

06:35.478 --> 06:37.647
I must insist

06:35.478 --> 06:37.647
that no one leave the room!

06:37.689 --> 06:39.858
Angela, I know things

06:37.689 --> 06:39.858
didn't go so well

06:39.900 --> 06:41.151
the last time,

06:41.193 --> 06:43.153
but I'm ready to try this again.

06:43.195 --> 06:44.612
Yes, Warren? Yes?

06:44.654 --> 06:47.824
We'll start our questioning

06:44.654 --> 06:47.824
with you, sir.

06:47.866 --> 06:51.286
If you've nothing to hide,

06:47.866 --> 06:51.286
you've nothing to fear!

06:51.328 --> 06:54.455
If you struggle, it'll only

06:51.328 --> 06:54.455
make it worse for you.

06:54.497 --> 06:56.457
Maybe I shouldn't

06:54.497 --> 06:56.457
have given him

06:56.499 --> 06:58.543
all the keys

06:56.499 --> 06:58.543
to the guest rooms.

07:06.218 --> 07:07.928
Dinner's going okay so far.

07:07.969 --> 07:09.470
Mr. Li seems nice.

07:09.512 --> 07:11.556
But my tongue is killing me.

07:11.598 --> 07:14.142
No one told me that putting

07:11.598 --> 07:14.142
a metal spike through it

07:14.184 --> 07:15.894
would be so uncomfortable.

07:15.936 --> 07:17.979
So, you two lovebirds met

07:15.936 --> 07:17.979
on a cruise.

07:18.021 --> 07:19.356
What was that like?

07:19.398 --> 07:21.482
What is this,

07:19.398 --> 07:21.482
the third degree?

07:21.524 --> 07:24.111
People meet.

07:21.524 --> 07:24.111
Happens every day.

07:24.152 --> 07:25.570
It's an interesting story.

07:25.612 --> 07:28.156
The woman I dined

07:25.612 --> 07:28.156
with the first night

07:28.198 --> 07:31.785
was confined to sickbay

07:28.198 --> 07:31.785
after she fell overboard.

07:33.036 --> 07:35.496
We had rough seas.

07:35.538 --> 07:37.374
LI:

07:35.538 --> 07:37.374
But as often happens,

07:37.416 --> 07:40.127
misfortune brings opportunity,

07:40.168 --> 07:44.505
for it was then

07:40.168 --> 07:44.505
I met the beautiful Ida.

07:44.547 --> 07:45.966
(chokes)

07:46.007 --> 07:48.218
Sorry. Swallowed a bug.

07:48.260 --> 07:49.428
Come on, Dewey.

07:49.469 --> 07:51.346
Have a dumpling.

07:49.469 --> 07:51.346
They're your favorite.

07:51.388 --> 07:53.098
And the only way

07:51.388 --> 07:53.098
you can get one

07:53.140 --> 07:54.599
is by taking it

07:53.140 --> 07:54.599
off this plate

07:54.641 --> 07:58.103
that I'm holding,

07:54.641 --> 07:58.103
