Who the hell is Jamie?

08:05.735 --> 08:07.487
Your grandson.

08:10.573 --> 08:12.575
Huh. We never named them

08:12.617 --> 08:15.454
till we were sure

08:12.617 --> 08:15.454
they would survive.

08:15.495 --> 08:16.537
(chuckles)

08:16.579 --> 08:18.206
I love this dark humor of hers.

08:18.248 --> 08:19.540
I'm telling you,

08:19.582 --> 08:21.709
you have nothing but fun

08:19.582 --> 08:21.709
ahead of you.

08:21.751 --> 08:24.379
Reese, this firecracker shrimp

08:21.751 --> 08:24.379
is fantastic.

08:24.421 --> 08:27.007
Yes. I didn't know you can get

08:24.421 --> 08:27.007
such hot peppers in America.

08:27.048 --> 08:29.009
(groans)

08:29.050 --> 08:30.218
Something wrong?

08:31.970 --> 08:34.931
I just realized that

08:31.970 --> 08:34.931
Grandma's really leaving!

08:34.973 --> 08:36.433
I need to be alone.

08:38.059 --> 08:40.520
You should get him a woman

08:38.059 --> 08:40.520
before it's too late.

08:41.271 --> 08:42.481
An ugly one.

08:42.563 --> 08:44.691
They're cheaper,

08:42.563 --> 08:44.691
they work harder.

08:47.819 --> 08:49.488
It's okay.

08:49.529 --> 08:51.490
I'm sure I had yellow goo

08:49.529 --> 08:51.490
coming out of my tongue

08:51.531 --> 08:52.782
before it got pierced.

08:52.824 --> 08:54.575
Drink your tea.

08:54.617 --> 08:56.453
You hate it when

08:54.617 --> 08:56.453
it gets cold.

08:56.495 --> 08:59.414
Oh, darling, you have

08:56.495 --> 08:59.414
something in your hair.

08:59.456 --> 09:00.415
What?

09:00.457 --> 09:01.666
Under your wig.

09:01.708 --> 09:03.460
What are you doing?!

09:01.708 --> 09:03.460
Get out of there!

09:04.127 --> 09:05.462
What is this?

09:06.338 --> 09:07.630
A list of my bank accounts...

09:07.672 --> 09:09.466
and the amounts in them.

09:12.427 --> 09:15.555
I had to know what

09:12.427 --> 09:15.555
I was getting into.

09:18.058 --> 09:20.519
Wise as well as beautiful.

09:20.560 --> 09:21.769
If we are going

09:20.560 --> 09:21.769
to get married,

09:21.811 --> 09:25.606
it is only fair you know

09:21.811 --> 09:25.606
how much money I have.

09:25.648 --> 09:27.650
If you're done tearing

09:25.648 --> 09:27.650
at me like a hyena,

09:27.692 --> 09:29.610
I have to go fix myself.

09:31.530 --> 09:32.655
Thank you so very much

09:32.697 --> 09:34.615
for allowing me

09:32.697 --> 09:34.615
into your home.

09:34.657 --> 09:37.118
Put on your makeup

09:34.657 --> 09:37.118
somewhere else, Nancy!

09:37.160 --> 09:42.623
So, I am just

09:37.160 --> 09:42.623
so incredibly curious.

09:42.665 --> 09:45.460
You're in love with... my mom?

09:45.502 --> 09:48.296
I know it seems strange

09:45.502 --> 09:48.296
to people.

09:48.338 --> 09:51.466
I know that we are

09:48.338 --> 09:51.466
so very different.

09:51.508 --> 09:53.634
But ever since

09:51.508 --> 09:53.634
I met your mother,

09:53.676 --> 09:56.012
I've...

09:56.054 --> 09:58.390
She just makes me happy.

09:58.932 --> 10:00.475
I'm the happiest

10:00.517 --> 10:03.562
I've ever been in my whole life.

10:04.896 --> 10:09.359
And "happy" in your culture

10:04.896 --> 10:09.359
means the same as...?

10:10.693 --> 10:11.652
(knocking)

10:11.694 --> 10:14.489
MAN:

10:11.694 --> 10:14.489
It's open.

10:14.531 --> 10:15.656
Ah, gentlemen.

10:15.698 --> 10:17.825
I was expecting

10:15.698 --> 10:17.825
my fellow thespians.

10:17.867 --> 10:19.702
We're going to add

10:17.867 --> 10:19.702
a few delicious wrinkles

10:19.744 --> 10:21.496
to the plot tomorrow.

10:21.538 --> 10:23.664
Actually, that is what

10:21.538 --> 10:23.664
we wanted to talk to you about.

10:23.706 --> 10:24.874
Uh-uh-uh.

10:24.916 --> 10:26.667
If you think I'm going

10:24.916 --> 10:26.667
to give away the ending,

10:26.709 --> 10:27.668
you're sadly mistaken.

10:27.710 --> 10:29.087
Although...

10:29.129 --> 10:31.756
(old lady voice):

10:29.129 --> 10:31.756
I might pay particular attention

10:31.798 --> 10:34.717
to the enigmatic Mrs. Pomfreet.

10:34.759 --> 10:37.554
Otto...

10:34.759 --> 10:37.554
I'm sorry.

10:34.759 --> 10:37.554
We have to cancel the show.

10:37.596 --> 10:39.180
(Scottish accent):

10:37.596 --> 10:39.180
Or Lord McGregor,

10:39.222 --> 10:40.098
the gruff, but...

10:40.140 --> 10:41.682
What?

