Oh, God, please don't fire us!

10:51.192 --> 10:52.944
If we lose this job, it's over.

10:52.986 --> 10:55.322
There's no place lower

10:52.986 --> 10:55.322
in show business we can go.

10:55.363 --> 10:56.697
If you think

10:55.363 --> 10:56.697
I'm bad at this,

10:56.739 --> 10:58.950
you should have seen me

10:56.739 --> 10:58.950
at the Dairy Queen.

