Please.

11:03.746 --> 11:07.417
Please? Please?!

11:08.376 --> 11:09.669
Please?

11:11.004 --> 11:12.380
Please?

11:14.757 --> 11:16.717
Please?

11:16.759 --> 11:18.719
I can't believe

11:16.759 --> 11:18.719
you didn't fire them.

11:18.761 --> 11:20.721
I remember him

11:18.761 --> 11:20.721
from Dairy Queen.

11:20.763 --> 11:22.723
He  was  bad.

11:25.977 --> 11:27.228
Oh, no, no, no.

11:27.270 --> 11:28.729
LOIS: Malcolm,

11:27.270 --> 11:28.729
quit messing around in there

11:28.771 --> 11:29.772
and get out here.

11:29.814 --> 11:31.316
We're leaving

11:29.814 --> 11:31.316
for the wedding.

11:31.358 --> 11:32.442
I'll be out in a minute.

