11:32.484 --> 11:33.734
Hold your horses.

11:33.776 --> 11:34.735
What?

11:34.777 --> 11:35.736
Nothing.

11:35.778 --> 11:37.238
(lisping):

11:35.778 --> 11:37.238
Horses...

11:37.280 --> 11:40.367
Oh, my God, it's swollen

11:37.280 --> 11:40.367
so much, I can't say my S's.

