Mom's going to kill me.

11:42.994 --> 11:45.830
Wait. I can hide it.

11:45.872 --> 11:50.168
I'll be careful... how I talk.

11:50.210 --> 11:54.005
And avoid...

11:50.210 --> 11:54.005
that letter completely.

11:54.047 --> 11:56.715
(lisping):

11:54.047 --> 11:56.715
Simple.

11:58.092 --> 12:00.761
Well, looks like all

11:58.092 --> 12:00.761
of Ida's friends showed up.

12:00.803 --> 12:02.597
Let's hope this thing

12:00.803 --> 12:02.597
starts soon.

12:02.639 --> 12:05.058
Hey, Malcolm, what time

12:02.639 --> 12:05.058
does the parking lot close?

12:05.099 --> 12:06.643
6:00, 6:30, 7:00?

12:07.810 --> 12:09.728
Military time,

12:07.810 --> 12:09.728
that would be 1900, Dad.

12:11.814 --> 12:14.150
Ah, here's the

12:11.814 --> 12:14.150
blushing bride!

12:14.192 --> 12:16.777
I'm sorry, the hotel doesn't

12:14.192 --> 12:16.777
allow smoking in here.

12:16.819 --> 12:18.154
Back off, you cow.

12:18.196 --> 12:19.989
This is my special day.

12:21.700 --> 12:22.950
Hal, do you think...?

12:22.992 --> 12:24.785
Lois, I know it's weird,

12:22.992 --> 12:24.785
but love is blind

12:24.827 --> 12:27.038
and it's none of our business,

12:24.827 --> 12:27.038
so we might as well

12:27.080 --> 12:29.290
just let it go, wish them well,

12:27.080 --> 12:29.290
and move on.

12:29.332 --> 12:30.709
I know I have.

12:32.502 --> 12:34.629
Okay, I admit I've been

12:32.502 --> 12:34.629
a crummy brother,

12:34.671 --> 12:36.673
and I shouldn't have

12:34.671 --> 12:36.673
smashed your ship,

12:36.715 --> 12:39.634
and I probably should have

12:36.715 --> 12:39.634
tried out that new choke hold

12:39.676 --> 12:42.262
on an animal before

12:39.676 --> 12:42.262
using it on you.

12:42.303 --> 12:44.847
So, anyway,

12:42.303 --> 12:44.847
I got you this.

12:44.889 --> 12:47.308
Oh, wow!

12:47.350 --> 12:48.851
That's so cool.

12:48.893 --> 12:50.437
And you can play

12:48.893 --> 12:50.437
against the robots

12:50.478 --> 12:52.021
or you join them

12:50.478 --> 12:52.021
and fight the mutants.

12:52.063 --> 12:53.607
I've always wanted this game.

12:53.648 --> 12:55.191
I can't believe it.

12:55.233 --> 12:57.277
And there's a trick to skip

12:55.233 --> 12:57.277
levels. Here, let me show you...

12:57.318 --> 13:01.114
Mom, I just found the exact

12:57.318 --> 13:01.114
game I wanted for my birthday

13:01.155 --> 13:03.116
just lying on this chair.

13:04.867 --> 13:07.036
How can he be so insensitive?

13:09.038 --> 13:11.541
Jamie?

13:16.588 --> 13:18.339
LI:

13:16.588 --> 13:18.339
Ah, my love.

13:18.381 --> 13:19.716
I almost forgot--

13:19.758 --> 13:22.218
my grandmother wore

13:19.758 --> 13:22.218
this very necklace

13:22.260 --> 13:23.720
on her wedding day.

13:23.762 --> 13:24.845
It's called

13:24.887 --> 13:26.139
Shuang Hsi,

13:26.180 --> 13:29.476
the Chinese symbol

13:26.180 --> 13:29.476
for double happiness.

13:29.517 --> 13:33.438
White people aren't impressed

13:29.517 --> 13:33.438
with this junk.

13:33.480 --> 13:35.565
You're not supposed

13:33.480 --> 13:35.565
to see me before the wedding.

13:35.607 --> 13:36.857
Go back to your room

13:36.899 --> 13:38.817
before someone mistakes

13:36.899 --> 13:38.817
you for a waiter!

13:39.902 --> 13:42.071
Whatever my bride wants.

13:42.113 --> 13:45.158
I'll see you in a little while.

13:53.374 --> 13:56.503
Oh, my God.

13:56.544 --> 13:57.878
Opiate,

13:57.920 --> 13:59.880
opiate, mood elevator,

13:59.922 --> 14:02.717
large mammal tranquilizer...

14:02.759 --> 14:04.594
He's not in love

14:02.759 --> 14:04.594
with her at all.

14:04.636 --> 14:06.596
She's got him drugged!

14:12.185 --> 14:13.894
Skies are clear at the airport.

14:13.936 --> 14:15.605
No problem with

14:13.936 --> 14:15.605
their flight leaving.

14:15.647 --> 14:16.939
I'm checking the freeways.

14:16.981 --> 14:17.898
Dad, Mom,

14:17.940 --> 14:19.900
I have to tell you...

14:19.942 --> 14:21.068
a thing.

14:21.110 --> 14:21.944
What?

14:21.986 --> 14:23.738
Grandma...

14:23.780 --> 14:25.406
be drugging...

14:25.448 --> 14:27.908
the man from China.

14:27.950 --> 14:28.951
What?

14:28.993 --> 14:30.911
Grandma be drugging

14:28.993 --> 14:30.911
the man from China.

14:30.953 --> 14:33.998
What the hell is this?

14:34.040 --> 14:35.958
Powerful mood elevator.

14:36.000 --> 14:37.335
A lot of them.

14:37.377 --> 14:39.170
Bottle after bottle

14:37.377 --> 14:39.170
after bottle.

14:39.212 --> 14:40.505
She's drugging him?

14:40.547 --> 14:41.922
How is she doing that?

14:41.964 --> 14:43.090
The tea.

14:43.132 --> 14:45.802
My God, of course,

14:43.132 --> 14:45.802
the tea!

14:45.844 --> 14:47.970
Remember, she kept

14:45.844 --> 14:47.970
refilling his cup all night.

14:48.012 --> 14:49.930
That's how I'd do it.

14:49.972 --> 14:52.975
You're sure that

14:49.972 --> 14:52.975
this is her purse?

14:53.017 --> 14:54.394
Ye...

14:54.435 --> 14:55.395
Affirmative.

14:55.436 --> 14:56.521
Oh, stop screwing around.

14:56.563 --> 14:57.480
Yes or no?

14:58.022 --> 14:59.440
Yes or no?!

14:59.482 --> 15:01.401
Not no.

15:01.442 --> 15:02.985
Stealing

15:03.027 --> 15:04.445
an old woman's purse.

15:04.487 --> 15:06.239
I should have you all arrested.

15:06.280 --> 15:09.158
Us? We know what you're doing

15:06.280 --> 15:09.158
to that poor Mr. Li.

15:09.200 --> 15:11.952
My God, I thought you were an

15:09.200 --> 15:11.952
evil, conniving monster before,

15:11.994 --> 15:14.414
but this, Mother,

15:11.994 --> 15:14.414
this is beyond the pale!

15:14.455 --> 15:15.956
HAL:

15:14.455 --> 15:15.956
He's a human being,

15:15.998 --> 15:17.792
and you're drugging him!

15:17.834 --> 15:19.252
It's called seduction.

15:19.293 --> 15:21.962
It's no different

15:19.293 --> 15:21.962
from wearing perfume

15:22.004 --> 15:24.758
or padding your bra

15:22.004 --> 15:24.758
with potatoes.

15:24.799 --> 15:27.427
What girl doesn't look

15:24.799 --> 15:27.427
for a little edge?

15:27.468 --> 15:29.387
You are out of your mind!

15:29.429 --> 15:30.805
Either you march up

15:30.847 --> 15:32.682
to his room and tell him

15:30.847 --> 15:32.682
this wedding is off

15:32.724 --> 15:34.058
or we're calling the police!

15:34.100 --> 15:37.978
All right, I'm going.

15:38.020 --> 15:39.021
Split the take?

15:39.063 --> 15:40.440
Mom, go!

15:42.400 --> 15:44.819
...and how could

15:42.400 --> 15:44.819
our murderer

15:44.861 --> 15:46.987
leave no footprints?

15:47.029 --> 15:50.825
Because I submit to you

15:50.867 --> 15:52.493
that he did not walk,

15:52.535 --> 15:54.454
but rather swung...

15:54.495 --> 15:58.082
into the room... on a rope!

15:58.124 --> 16:03.003
And the only

15:58.124 --> 16:03.003
former circus acrobat here is...

16:03.045 --> 16:04.422
That man!

16:05.047 --> 16:06.883
And... that woman!

16:06.925 --> 16:07.967
(gasps)

16:09.510 --> 16:11.512
Oh, Edward, the game's up.

16:11.554 --> 16:14.390
(Cockney accent):

16:11.554 --> 16:14.390
Yeah, we done it.

16:14.432 --> 16:17.268
And we'd do it again, Guv'ner.

16:17.310 --> 16:20.980
Mystery solved.

16:23.483 --> 16:25.902
Oh, bravo!

16:27.737 --> 16:29.614
Oh, my God.

16:29.656 --> 16:30.865
Did you feel that?

16:30.907 --> 16:32.032
It was wonderful!

16:32.074 --> 16:33.910
That was the best reaction

16:32.074 --> 16:33.910
we've ever had.

16:33.952 --> 16:35.035
Thank you so much.

16:35.077 --> 16:36.913
Thank you for giving us

16:35.077 --> 16:36.913
this chance.

16:36.955 --> 16:38.205
No need.

16:38.247 --> 16:40.040
The important thing is you

16:38.247 --> 16:40.040
believed in yourself

16:40.082 --> 16:41.876
and you did a great job.

16:41.918 --> 16:43.670
(stilted):

16:41.918 --> 16:43.670
What a delightful display

16:43.711 --> 16:45.546
of intrigue and whimsy.

16:46.589 --> 16:47.841
(reciting):

16:46.589 --> 16:47.841
I will remember this

16:47.882 --> 16:49.049
for years to come.

16:49.091 --> 16:51.177
I cannot wait

16:49.091 --> 16:51.177
to tell my friends.

16:52.512 --> 16:54.472
(chuckling)

16:54.514 --> 16:56.265
You hired the audience?

16:56.307 --> 16:58.768
I hated to see him

16:56.307 --> 16:58.768
so depressed.

16:58.810 --> 17:01.437
Within its framework

16:58.810 --> 17:01.437
of commitment and loyalty,

17:01.479 --> 17:05.065
marriage enables

17:01.479 --> 17:05.065
the establishment of a home...

17:05.107 --> 17:07.443
They look so

17:05.107 --> 17:07.443
nice together.

17:07.485 --> 17:09.236
Yeah, they do.

17:09.278 --> 17:11.322
I just love weddings.

17:11.364 --> 17:13.783
...with trust and patience,

17:11.364 --> 17:13.783
your love will grow stronger.

17:13.825 --> 17:15.702
Weren't we supposed

17:13.825 --> 17:15.702
to stop this?

17:15.743 --> 17:17.745
Hmm. I think you're right.

17:17.787 --> 17:19.079
I wonder why we didn't.

17:19.121 --> 17:20.331
Who cares?

17:20.373 --> 17:21.791
It's nice.

17:21.833 --> 17:23.459
Oh, I'm not

17:21.833 --> 17:23.459
worried about it.

17:23.501 --> 17:26.170
I... I'm just... happy.

17:26.212 --> 17:28.464
MINISTER: Your love and respect

17:26.212 --> 17:28.464
for each other,

17:28.506 --> 17:30.466
your trust and understanding

17:28.506 --> 17:30.466
of each other

17:30.508 --> 17:32.719
will increase

17:30.508 --> 17:32.719
your contentment...

17:32.760 --> 17:34.804
They're all empty.

17:34.846 --> 17:36.014
Every bottle.

17:36.055 --> 17:37.932
She drugged us all.

17:37.974 --> 17:40.643
That filthy,

17:37.974 --> 17:40.643
hateful monster.

17:43.145 --> 17:44.146
But how'd she do it?

17:44.188 --> 17:46.106
The buffet.

17:46.148 --> 17:48.108
Oh, that's right.

17:48.150 --> 17:50.820
It showed up right after

17:48.150 --> 17:50.820
she went to talk to Mr. Li.

17:50.862 --> 17:52.196
That evil genius.

17:52.238 --> 17:54.532
You know, she knew we couldn't

17:52.238 --> 17:54.532
pass up free food.

17:54.574 --> 17:56.784
This is simply the

17:54.574 --> 17:56.784
most diabolical,

17:56.826 --> 17:58.995
hateful thing

17:56.826 --> 17:58.995
she's ever done.

17:59.037 --> 18:02.289
But I sure do like

17:59.037 --> 18:02.289
her dress. Don't you?

18:02.331 --> 18:03.791
I agree.

18:03.833 --> 18:07.127
It's weird-- I used to

18:03.833 --> 18:07.127
just think thoughts.

18:07.169 --> 18:09.964
Now my thoughts

18:07.169 --> 18:09.964
are thinking thoughts.

18:10.006 --> 18:13.426
It's like, if I don't exist,

18:10.006 --> 18:13.426
who's saying if I don't exist?

18:13.467 --> 18:14.761
You know what I mean?

18:14.802 --> 18:17.931
I'll tell you who's saying it.

18:17.972 --> 18:19.390
Me.

18:19.432 --> 18:22.518
It's like I think, therefore...

18:22.560 --> 18:24.854
Oh, wait.

18:24.896 --> 18:26.313
I had it.

18:26.355 --> 18:28.608
Don't worry, Reese,

18:26.355 --> 18:28.608
it'll come back around.

18:28.649 --> 18:29.609
Yeah.

18:29.650 --> 18:32.403
Hey, you spoke to me.

18:32.445 --> 18:33.571
I exist.

18:33.613 --> 18:34.864
For now.

18:34.906 --> 18:35.990
MINISTER:

18:34.906 --> 18:35.990
...buds are yet to blossom

18:36.032 --> 18:37.157
and with care...

18:37.199 --> 18:38.785
You know, I have to admit,

18:38.826 --> 18:41.621
part of me wishes we could

18:38.826 --> 18:41.621
just stay this happy forever.

18:41.662 --> 18:45.165
Can we, Malcolm?

18:41.662 --> 18:45.165
Can we?

18:45.207 --> 18:46.375
Not really.

18:46.417 --> 18:48.252
(lisping):

18:46.417 --> 18:48.252
I mean, most of these drugs

18:48.294 --> 18:50.170
wear off

18:48.294 --> 18:50.170
after four or five hours.

18:50.212 --> 18:51.589
Malcolm, why

18:50.212 --> 18:51.589
are you lisping?

18:51.631 --> 18:53.424
I pierced my tongue.

18:53.466 --> 18:56.176
I've been hiding it because

18:53.466 --> 18:56.176
I knew you'd go psycho.

18:56.218 --> 18:58.345
I'll show you psycho.

18:58.387 --> 19:01.057
When we get home, I'm going

18:58.387 --> 19:01.057
to pull that thing out

19:01.099 --> 19:02.224
with a pair of pliers.

19:02.266 --> 19:04.184
Sounds fair.

19:04.226 --> 19:06.771
Be constant and consistent

19:04.226 --> 19:06.771
in your love.

19:06.813 --> 19:08.355
From this comes the knowledge

19:08.397 --> 19:11.275
that you can

19:08.397 --> 19:11.275
weather any storm...

19:11.317 --> 19:13.193
Did you drink your tea?

19:13.235 --> 19:14.112
What tea?

19:14.153 --> 19:15.113
The tea I gave you

19:15.154 --> 19:16.238
right before the ceremony.

19:16.280 --> 19:17.573
Oh, I'm sorry.

19:17.615 --> 19:20.076
I thought that was for me.

19:20.118 --> 19:22.202
Did anyone ever tell you,

19:22.244 --> 19:25.205
you have a beautiful smile?

19:25.247 --> 19:26.874
I haven't been

19:25.247 --> 19:26.874
to the dentist in years.

19:26.916 --> 19:28.375
I should really

19:26.916 --> 19:28.375
give him a call...

19:28.417 --> 19:30.210
Get on with it, God boy!

19:30.252 --> 19:33.923
Well, someone's eager for the

19:30.252 --> 19:33.923
sacrament of married love, huh?

19:33.965 --> 19:35.215
(chuckling)

19:35.257 --> 19:37.010
I think Mr. Li's

19:35.257 --> 19:37.010
coming out of it.

19:37.051 --> 19:38.260
Ah, what a shame.

19:38.302 --> 19:40.680
The old bat used up

19:38.302 --> 19:40.680
all her happy pills on us.

19:40.721 --> 19:42.056
Oh, also,

19:42.098 --> 19:45.267
this is so very, very,

19:42.098 --> 19:45.267
very important.

19:45.309 --> 19:46.894
Never go to bed angry.

19:46.936 --> 19:49.605
I should say,

19:46.936 --> 19:49.605
never go to sleep angry.

19:49.647 --> 19:51.482
(laughs)

19:51.524 --> 19:53.442
And you know what?

19:53.484 --> 19:54.694
Never eat salad angry.

19:54.735 --> 19:56.154
Never eat soup sad.

19:56.195 --> 19:57.905
Give me these.

19:57.947 --> 19:59.115
Here.

19:59.157 --> 20:00.240
Go.

20:00.282 --> 20:01.492
Shall we pray...?

20:00.282 --> 20:01.492
No!

20:01.534 --> 20:03.243
All righty then.

20:01.534 --> 20:03.243
Do you take...?

20:03.285 --> 20:04.162
Yes!

20:04.203 --> 20:05.245
And do you...?

20:05.287 --> 20:06.246
Yes!

20:06.288 --> 20:07.707
Then I now pronounce you...

20:07.748 --> 20:09.291
Who the hell are you?

20:10.501 --> 20:12.503
Oh, darling, don't be silly.

20:12.545 --> 20:13.838
Get the rings!

20:13.880 --> 20:16.256
Wait, I know you.

20:16.298 --> 20:18.425
You're that horrible woman

20:16.298 --> 20:18.425
at my table

20:18.467 --> 20:20.260
who kept spitting

20:18.467 --> 20:20.260
at the busboys.

20:20.302 --> 20:22.262
Oh, no, no.

20:20.302 --> 20:22.262
That was someone else.

20:22.304 --> 20:23.347
No, it was you!

20:23.389 --> 20:24.515
My little honey lamb.

20:24.557 --> 20:26.266
Let me go!

20:24.557 --> 20:26.266
Hoochie-coochie.

20:26.308 --> 20:27.935
(Li speaking Cantonese)

20:27.977 --> 20:29.311
Ow! Ooh!

20:29.353 --> 20:30.312
Ooh!

20:30.354 --> 20:31.438
You take your...

20:31.480 --> 20:33.315
take your hands

20:31.480 --> 20:33.315
off of me!

20:33.357 --> 20:36.694
You can't leave me now!

20:36.736 --> 20:39.072
I'm pregnant! Oh!

20:39.113 --> 20:41.281
(sobbing)

20:41.323 --> 20:43.283
Why, why?!

20:43.325 --> 20:46.579
Why can't I ever be happy?!

20:46.620 --> 20:47.914
(crying)

20:47.955 --> 20:51.417
I promised I wasn't

20:47.955 --> 20:51.417
going to do this.

20:52.585 --> 20:54.003
There's still dirt

20:52.585 --> 20:54.003
under the rim.

20:54.045 --> 20:55.379
I've been scrubbing

20:54.045 --> 20:55.379
for an hour.

20:55.421 --> 20:56.964
It's not coming off.

20:57.006 --> 20:58.966
Well, since you don't care

20:57.006 --> 20:58.966
about your tongue,

20:59.008 --> 21:01.177
maybe you could use that

20:59.008 --> 21:01.177
to clean the toilet.

21:01.219 --> 21:02.595
I found Grandma's thermos.

21:04.388 --> 21:06.224
Looks like there's still

21:04.388 --> 21:06.224
a half cup left

21:06.265 --> 21:07.307
of this terrible potion.

21:07.349 --> 21:09.018
You know, the lawnmower

21:07.349 --> 21:09.018
